OOC: Sorry out of town also I was told the Cf would let me use the CR 
chambers

::Koj::

Koj lands and helps Inu-yasha in to the CF in to a CR Chamber to heal.

::Inu-Yasha::

Shuts down while he repairs.

::Koj::

Koj looking at his own wounds and feels unease steps into a Chamber and goes 
off line to heal.

                          ::The Past::

::Koj::

Koj the gaint Decepticons stares at the stars "Decepticons never look at the 
stars unless we are choosing which planet to conquer."

::Lilly::

As she lay her head on  Koj chest "When this war is over we can travel the 
stars together"

::Koj::

Koj as gently pats her head "A Autobot and a Decepticon never has there been 
quite a pair." Laughing as he picked up the lute and started to play.

::Lilly::

Lilly looking at him "What did you tell Galvatron?"

::Koj::

Koj stops playing "I'm one of his elite 6 he never questions me?"

::Laserbeak::

Laserbeak flying high recording everything.
